lead_paragraph: In her WTA Tour debut, Madison Keys, 14, upset Alla Kudryavtseva of Russia, 7-5, 6-4, in the opening round of The MPS Group Championships in Ponte Vedra Beach, Fla.Kudryavtseva is ranked 81st.
